snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Sister Location - Mobile Update
snippet.description:
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/five-nights-at-freddys-sister-location/id1189781891

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.scottgames.sisterlocation

A new update is live for Sister Location on mobile devices (version 2.0.2 - Android & version 2.0.1 - iOS). Check out the following changes!

- Subtitles in 11 languages ( Interface and audio in English. Subtitles in English, French, German,    Dutch, Spanish (Latin America), Italian, Portuguese (Brazil), Russian, Japanese, Chinese (Simplified), Korean.)
- Improved audio support [android]
- Fixed the pan of some audio samples [ios]
- Improved virtual controller
- Revamped vibrations
- Various fixes and improvements

Please subscribe to our channel!

#FNaF #MadeWithFusion
